{"tid":728680,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【小米上市】消息指，小米（０１８１０）一手中籤率１００％","createTime":"2018-07-04T02:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T16:11:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf566df1e2001122b2358fb9f4bad633f6da1967","tid":728680,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"　《經濟通通訊社４日專訊》本港首隻「同股不同權」的新股小米（０１８１０）將於下周一（９日）掛牌，市場消息指，一手中籤率１００％，即人人有份，逾２﹒５萬人申請一手；至於獲分派２手有１﹒５萬人，認購９手穩獲２手。<br />\n<br />\n　　而Ｂ組的大戶方面，最大一張飛為認購１０００萬股，獲分９７﹒２萬股。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前已傳小米以１７元下限定價，而最新消息指，機構投資者昨日（３日）已在暗盤（ＧｒｅｙＭａｒｋｅｔ）進行交易，以每股１６﹒１５元成交，較招股定價１７元低５％，涉資２８００萬美元（約２﹒２億港元）。（ｍｌ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036e2327d34560e17abb832f66bf8b366d6bb876","tid":728680,"uid":186594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c20d18284789a08c4562ed0651b95a00b1bfcd6","tid":728680,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7568b21533c18d8d2a887b30d23bb4a21604171e","tid":728680,"uid":81150